Add Privacy Sandbox attestation list and manifest file. This allows
component updater to read the pre-installed attestation list if the
newest version has not been downloaded yet.

A histogram is added to record when an attestation check takes place,
whether the attestation map is parsed from a bundled or a downloaded
attestation file.

